{"tid":356091,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓義工係世界上最善良嘅人","createTime":"2017-08-11T19:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T19:17:39.000Z","uid":103534,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"003f3aafb1ffeacdf5087a222d69b34f638ac252","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T19:33:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你個咀，利用人嘅愛心用大話去搵錢，即使係用晌貓身上我都覺得好可恥！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本身我對貓義工嘅睇法係由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說前兩個月我想領養多隻貓，於是就上網搵，希望以領養為先。搵左好耐，就遇到呢個貓義工，佢話隻貓係晌繁殖場用2000救佢翻黎，所以準領養者要比翻2000領養費。<br />\n<br />\n當時我覺得比2000唔係問題，所以約左時間去到佢到探隻貓。去到時發現貓咪好瘦，又怕人，於是問下貓義工貓咪有冇咩健康問題，佢只係答我啱啱翻黎，未蠹蟲，又少食野，所以咁瘦。我當時冇懷疑，百份百信佢講嘅野。因為本身都打算領養完會帶貓咪去做個簡單檢查，所以覺得冇乜問題。<br />\n<br />\n但翻到屋企諗清楚後，都係決定唔領養呢隻貓。<br />\n<br />\n直到過左個幾月後，見到呢個post 我就火都黎埋，話隻貓7月係好心婆婆晌街執翻黎，又生腫瘤，要帶佢睇醫生，叫人捐錢。於是我cap翻之前佢嘅對話放晌佢個page，點知佢delete我個留言加對話相。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>騙徒嘅手法真係層出不窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/033314_8e254f799e2ea04637da67176fefefed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F033314_8e254f799e2ea04637da67176fefefed.jpg&h=aa08a467&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/033316_8e254f799e2ea04637da67176fefefed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F033316_8e254f799e2ea04637da67176fefefed.jpg&h=a1568364&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/033317_4d5c093f12bdc41d94b74ce0c7e78c1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F033317_4d5c093f12bdc41d94b74ce0c7e78c1b.jpg&h=f20340d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6f01bb029dac4804054979c7e883ee8b5378fd","tid":356091,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T19:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名跟進"},{"pid":"9994d016e7569e7963aa66eee26d1e8f39a04d04","tid":356091,"uid":135840,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T19:51:53.000Z","msg":"（認真）<br />\n經過長時間嘅接觸，發現大部分異工都有精神病。有好多都活係自己個世界，好似同外界點都係有少少偏差咁。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e128c78ec6a18f15709eb141536f7af3764035d","tid":356091,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T23:11:02.000Z","msg":"屌 佢地真係on9"},{"pid":"dbe17db7530ffb3bc52e06897ebb1565275d8c09","tid":356091,"uid":57494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"即係6月喺佢屋企搵領養7月喺街執？  叫佢睇下精神科好喎？  呃人嘅開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913b45f3272cb78b9b8b9725599b14d9be45fef2","tid":356091,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"寵物店收錢賣貓扮領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6b336002f3f8068def4c3a3a37bf3ad525b717","tid":356091,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"d0ea124ed77963c43d4a5eec1defc2075b6573f7","tid":356091,"uid":16333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁仆街都有嘅"},{"pid":"e7b91411c65979c478d4b90d5f9da159ffc4dd9a","tid":356091,"uid":1505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:26:16.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"39cbc65428b509367269c411c70ead38df6f72e1","tid":356091,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:38:27.000Z","msg":"做得呢d通常都痴痴地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d72d1e5b1e75e675a558210d2e4eb5531d516b","tid":356091,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"啲貓group有人仲話<br />\n義工係自願性質 冇必要公開條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1b0a85202c2ffaaed6c40c5b5b223b1fc3ff94","tid":356091,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"啲義工好撚搞笑 自己無能力又執咁多傷病貓 然後就上網籌錢 當自己慈善機構？"},{"pid":"11e2bf62bb5096050aa7481b04e328c5ab136952","tid":356091,"uid":135207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"開名啦，咁樣先至唔會再有人受騙，嚇一下其他想借人善心去呃錢嘅假義工。"},{"pid":"b8e3e7301ff7a08724fbe861e5316857fb2abfda","tid":356091,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T02:00:32.000Z","msg":"開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5415fdfaa05b2bf525dca9385ad6545456e9440d","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/103406_84a0f3bda7545958bbfea21496ce0709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F103406_84a0f3bda7545958bbfea21496ce0709.jpg&h=2d9d3a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔洗遮啦 佢較公開 係人都睇到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一搵就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89f0d376f168d53fa1a5ae64a91d035320860ad","tid":356091,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"求開名"},{"pid":"7847831544331a6bd898522e5da3362db668381b","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/104102_be9176056ae8d325d1a3d2573d9704e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F104102_be9176056ae8d325d1a3d2573d9704e1.jpg&h=9da22103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真身係佢？ <br />\n我見佢個大篇野 下款寫依個acc名 同埋佢有話咩退款留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地而家要退款比捐錢人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f567dadaec116eade0285965f81667b9c25c1ea","tid":356091,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"開始淆底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3499646c0667ddf25607e340ca63d5cd3dc54278","tid":356091,"uid":21654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"係另一個人開post話呢個義工3個月問人10次捐錢，比左幾千蚊，覺得受騙同滋擾開post問人點<br />\n當時個post無開名，上面嗰個當時人主動話退款，成個post都係撐義工，事主話佢明顯收多左醫嗰隻貓嘅錢都唔出聲話夠，撐義工嘅即刻話多左嘅錢咪救下一隻，唔覺得有問題，咁多人撐佢會淆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算樓主post去天貓都唔會有人撐，嗰個係義工港豬場佔多數"},{"pid":"c1f355e11cbabfa76edf6c9d52b21ad01b139f6e","tid":356091,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"咁都唔開名你開咩post<br />\n都係收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c38e48d4f9f8d92e81e2aa5e898d6c9c407e30","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:42:20.000Z","msg":"可能佢地真係有用到啲錢去幫貓，不過唔需要作咁嘅故仔。領養本身要比成2000，我不如出去買？當時我打算比呢2000，真係當係支持下貓義工。諗起都燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9fbd8d22f65950f76846b11fed5e4f0ed5191f","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係另一個人開post話呢個義工3個月問人10次捐錢，比左幾千蚊，覺得受騙同滋擾開post問人點<br />\n當時個post無開名，上面嗰個當時人主動話退款，成個post都係撐義工，事主話佢明顯收多左醫嗰隻貓嘅錢都唔出聲話夠，撐義工嘅即刻話多左嘅錢咪救下一隻，唔覺得有問題，咁多人撐佢會淆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算樓主post去天貓都唔會有人撐，嗰個係義工港豬場佔多數</blockquote><br />\n呢到又係見到佢地on9，盲撐嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c52d62f431359dad4edd1ff2746a0342fd0413","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物店收錢賣貓扮領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又未必係寵物店嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6df7842fa98d281d08862ef6c92064dac87cc70","tid":356091,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"2d7f08b43d81ca930b1c965b7ccbfd40f625a11c","tid":356091,"uid":138821,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開名啦</blockquote><br />\n我見個義工好多人撐佢<br />\n唔似樓主請到咁！相反樓主睇完貓仲好似好慶幸自己無領養到而沾沾自喜，黑心到核爆！"},{"pid":"17d196b93af511790956c75f32b2f1dcefa05ead","tid":356091,"uid":138821,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開名啦</blockquote><br />\n我見個義工好多人撐佢<br />\n唔似樓主請到咁！相反樓主睇完貓仲好似好慶幸自己無領養到而沾沾自喜，黑心到核爆！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/231505_86729ee586774ef7235b7314d545d85c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F231505_86729ee586774ef7235b7314d545d85c.jpg&h=56eb8352&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/231506_86729ee586774ef7235b7314d545d85c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F231506_86729ee586774ef7235b7314d545d85c.jpg&h=b5a234f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/231506_d0b33e3127fa1c634a8ae353395a4995.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F231506_d0b33e3127fa1c634a8ae353395a4995.jpg&h=10d97f48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f763f94016bc17b3767593b3ee302b8327d3b0d4","tid":356091,"uid":138821,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係另一個人開post話呢個義工3個月問人10次捐錢，比左幾千蚊，覺得受騙同滋擾開post問人點<br />\n當時個post無開名，上面嗰個當時人主動話退款，成個post都係撐義工，事主話佢明顯收多左醫嗰隻貓嘅錢都唔出聲話夠，撐義工嘅即刻話多左嘅錢咪救下一隻，唔覺得有問題，咁多人撐佢會淆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算樓主post去天貓都唔會有人撐，嗰個係義工港豬場佔多數</blockquote><br />\n呢到又係見到佢地on9，盲撐嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/233441_f71e263aff5bd4d76f908d6c0ff9e790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F233441_f71e263aff5bd4d76f908d6c0ff9e790.jpg&h=3a139b33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/233441_20e94fbf6010d703833760dcca56c0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F233441_20e94fbf6010d703833760dcca56c0e1.jpg&h=b3531668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩個就係領養人出爾反爾，無人迫佢捐錢，捐左就問人攞番，誠信破產！呢d人先恐怖！又要威又要帶頭盔！"},{"pid":"e572fbcc9a51b8e6c8d2bc0565c343afdbbb37ee","tid":356091,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b151b3f40740f19266a13727a3804c8ee822f015","tid":356091,"uid":38304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:51:24.000Z","msg":"你係義工?"},{"pid":"bd2aae3d563756518a16de8aba059b4ff0b0911b","tid":356091,"uid":3757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:59:58.000Z","msg":"義工出沒注意<br />\n<br />\n捐錢會俾人起底<br />\n<br />\n你捐埋我個份"},{"pid":"7d89df75491b49a1ba950923aa2506ea113c62e3","tid":356091,"uid":11392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係義工?</blockquote><br />\n好明顯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a876657da57b162f103ad505dffe416df7305a7","tid":356091,"uid":138821,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係義工?</blockquote><br />\n好明顯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係義工囉！唔洗做義工先可以有分析能力！天貓果到義工有同果樓主老婆解釋過的，你地先係盲撐樓主囉！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/081236_8562bee3fd0736dec35a53d77abe2fd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F081236_8562bee3fd0736dec35a53d77abe2fd6.jpg&h=a895d631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/081236_97e29852e3861c2e1baceaca5969c5a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F081236_97e29852e3861c2e1baceaca5969c5a2.jpg&h=d485e992&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7f970721dd4ae9b7a9e5dc63bce193f86a3d1ce","tid":356091,"uid":44945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:24:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係義工?</blockquote><br />\n好明顯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係義工囉！唔洗做義工先可以有分析能力！天貓果到義工有同果樓主老婆解釋過的，你地先係盲撐樓主囉！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/081236_8562bee3fd0736dec35a53d77abe2fd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F081236_8562bee3fd0736dec35a53d77abe2fd6.jpg&h=a895d631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/081236_97e29852e3861c2e1baceaca5969c5a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F081236_97e29852e3861c2e1baceaca5969c5a2.jpg&h=d485e992&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，收嗲啦"},{"pid":"e2f0fc968c1c87a21582d8be4ecbd4904a0a956b","tid":356091,"uid":83062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:40:26.000Z","msg":"繁殖場畀錢救同買貓有咩分別？"},{"pid":"9f2501fe844b1db2730c203399b0c3e7df360f50","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:47:14.000Z","msg":"義工收收皮先啦 有心救就拎自己錢 冇錢又要救 <br />\n到冇錢就搵人乞 <br />\n你地個撚個都係咁 <br />\n好啲果啲都會話啲錢用左係邊<br />\n有啲直情收左錢就消失<br />\n<br />\n平時就當晒啲申請領養既人係狗<br />\n但冇錢有要搵水魚落搭<br />\n垃圾<br />\n<br />\n攬撚住啲貓過世啦 啲貓比你地「救」完又咪係住個爛鬼兩呎籠 食埋啲垃圾糧<br />\n係比繁殖場環境好少少既<br />\n但有人要又唔放手 你地真係誤左隻貓一生喇<br />\n貓義工 咪撚再害貓喇 放過佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e10d75569b6764d3593dc67f67b522aea47a3e","tid":356091,"uid":124322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:48:18.000Z","msg":"想問下上面條貓異工 點解寧願放番啲貓去街咁危險都唔比人領養？<br />\n執完嗰啲貓屋企有幾大地方比佢長期活動？點解寧願比佢地困住喺咁細既籠都唔比有心既人領養？"},{"pid":"6bb480eae31ba6e34200b3dff240276e70461dc2","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下上面條貓異工 點解寧願放番啲貓去街咁危險都唔比人領養？<br />\n執完嗰啲貓屋企有幾大地方比佢長期活動？點解寧願比佢地困住喺咁細既籠都唔比有心既人領養？</blockquote><br />\n偽善者 <br />\n之後就會屌你地班仆街唔自己落手落腳救貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd2472ef4a507b679bf77aab931b31226815bc9","tid":356091,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"就係佢地愈來愈多人買貓都唔去領養"},{"pid":"3dd940b0275c29fdd1fce1d629c24327ad2db71b","tid":356091,"uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下上面條貓異工 點解寧願放番啲貓去街咁危險都唔比人領養？<br />\n執完嗰啲貓屋企有幾大地方比佢長期活動？點解寧願比佢地困住喺咁細既籠都唔比有心既人領養？</blockquote><br />\n偽善者 <br />\n之後就會屌你地班仆街唔自己落手落腳救貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰班異工最鍾意唔夠人講就「你自己去救囉」<br />\n講到無救過貓就唔可以出聲質疑佢地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb343652125f6e8f070c73d6e6e0b30012afd7d5","tid":356091,"uid":124322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下上面條貓異工 點解寧願放番啲貓去街咁危險都唔比人領養？<br />\n執完嗰啲貓屋企有幾大地方比佢長期活動？點解寧願比佢地困住喺咁細既籠都唔比有心既人領養？</blockquote><br />\n偽善者 <br />\n之後就會屌你地班仆街唔自己落手落腳救貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰班異工最鍾意唔夠人講就「你自己去救囉」<br />\n講到無救過貓就唔可以出聲質疑佢地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人質疑下就話你地自己餵街貓執啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ad81e6eb1aade3a6f50650ef4a79c77ac9003a","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"好心冇咁大個頭唔好戴咁大頂帽啦<br />\n非洲夠多細路就死啦 又唔見佢地周圍問人乞再去捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話捉左人地返黎會比頭安穩住家就話姐<br />\n你捉到人地返黎就困籠 可能佢心諗 我係野外都唔會餓死 但有自由 係異工度就食得唔好又住得唔好<br />\n<br />\n人坐監都會提供三餐既 又得閒放下風<br />\n但d街貓做錯咩 要捉返佢比佢地折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n錯就錯在出現係班19異工前面"},{"pid":"18865d56c07bda0b7b757af6fdb6984d84d034c7","tid":356091,"uid":133988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"夠疆就垃圾貓義工入黎面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌撚到佢反皮"},{"pid":"89c5477c9149e5d1ee411b05883858f6324ecd21","tid":356091,"uid":28129,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n佢上水講野:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kuromi.tungtung/posts/10207674472499722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkuromi.tungtung%2Fposts%2F10207674472499722&d=BGzdSWcpVg%2FRzrXWWL2Ys4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=96b4c95b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kuromi.tungtung/posts/10207674472499722</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/102314_9d9c6a3c4f30f0c32cd358f88858ef0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F102314_9d9c6a3c4f30f0c32cd358f88858ef0f.jpg&h=a9df4b61&s={SIZE}\" />。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/102316_399f7bb8d217a8bde403c7265e64e002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F102316_399f7bb8d217a8bde403c7265e64e002.jpg&h=8ea5b47a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4100913a50a59c6ec0fab27140c032da269d07c2","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"bf256e3f0464ce95bd7c321ae1d470467fd46de0","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"一排冇上黎，竟然係咁。其實我唔開名大家都見到係邊個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我聽老婆話，唔再追究呢件事，點知有人上黎玩自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我沾沾自喜慶幸自己冇要隻貓？你冇病呀嘛，你如果有講清楚貓仔情況，我接受叫心甘情願。你冇講清楚，我事後發現，呢啲叫受騙。<br />\n呢件事上，我已cap好晒圖，要玩嘅，我準備好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74f91395e69a192690ddc804ddf5b20c35b3a62","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n佢上水講野:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kuromi.tungtung/posts/10207674472499722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkuromi.tungtung%2Fposts%2F10207674472499722&d=BGzdSWcpVg%2FRzrXWWL2Ys4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=96b4c95b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kuromi.tungtung/posts/10207674472499722</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/102314_9d9c6a3c4f30f0c32cd358f88858ef0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F102314_9d9c6a3c4f30f0c32cd358f88858ef0f.jpg&h=a9df4b61&s={SIZE}\" />。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/102316_399f7bb8d217a8bde403c7265e64e002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F102316_399f7bb8d217a8bde403c7265e64e002.jpg&h=8ea5b47a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n算鳩數吧啦，人地退唔退錢我地冇捐嘅又理唔到。不過原來搵到隻病貓翻黎，作幾個感人嘅故仔出黎就有人捐錢，何樂而不為。作完故仔，前言不對後語都有一班同好異工撐，怕閪你地班友仔屌佢地咩。我發誓領養寵物一定唔再搵異工，唔係生仔冇屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705b20736951b01fe1e662e80e0d6dbda8fd109f","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"屌，我宜家怕咩同你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來貓異工一句不合就合公開埋人地啲资料架？咁大家以后捐钱前预左掉落海先，因为追人条数系会比人公开埋个名。异工好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6562451d06cfb2f8cde96964971a7ab1449b35f","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，我宜家怕咩同你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來貓異工一句不合就合公開埋人地啲<span style=\"color: red;\">资</span>料架？咁大家以后捐钱前预左掉落海先，因为追<span style=\"color: red;\">人条</span>数系会比人公开埋个名。异工好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩野變晒殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bf4b84d8f842fde10a9ec1e1197dc0c5d729ff","tid":356091,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813a7c4d384656a0b22b0132e02a1d88a9bfaca4","tid":356091,"uid":103534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係另一個人開post話呢個義工3個月問人10次捐錢，比左幾千蚊，覺得受騙同滋擾開post問人點<br />\n當時個post無開名，上面嗰個當時人主動話退款，成個post都係撐義工，事主話佢明顯收多左醫嗰隻貓嘅錢都唔出聲話夠，撐義工嘅即刻話多左嘅錢咪救下一隻，唔覺得有問題，咁多人撐佢會淆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算樓主post去天貓都唔會有人撐，嗰個係義工港豬場佔多數</blockquote><br />\n呢到又係見到佢地on9，盲撐嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/233441_f71e263aff5bd4d76f908d6c0ff9e790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F233441_f71e263aff5bd4d76f908d6c0ff9e790.jpg&h=3a139b33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/233441_20e94fbf6010d703833760dcca56c0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F233441_20e94fbf6010d703833760dcca56c0e1.jpg&h=b3531668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩個就係領養人出爾反爾，無人迫佢捐錢，捐左就問人攞番，誠信破產！呢d人先恐怖！又要威又要帶頭盔！</blockquote><br />\n陰公，捐完錢仲要比人開名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}